# Requirements

* eMMC 8-bit mode
* SD/MMC 1, 2 and 4-bit mode
* SPI compatible
* Must be libre BSD or MIT Licensed (no restrictions, no non-free "non-commercial" clauses).
* AXI interface preferred, Wishbone acceptable (bridge will be used).
